description:
I'm sending the following body:

'image' : {
                'name' : 'backup',
                'server' : {
                    'serverRef' : 32                
                }
            }

The response is 400: Expected serverRef attribute on server entity. Either the OSAPI 1.1 spec is incorrect or this is a bug.

